## Fluxo de Dados

```
1. Page SSR (app/page.tsx)
   в†“ fetch server-side (serverApi)
2. Client Component ({Feature}Client.tsx)
   в†“ props com dados SSR
3. Provider (use-{feature}-context.tsx)
   в†“ nuqs (URL state) + TanStack Query + Context
4. UI Components (DataGrid, Filters, Modals)
   в†“ useXxxContext() para acessar dados
5. API Resources (lib/api/resources/)
   в†“ Axios requests
6. Backend (redd-api)
```

## PadrГЈo de Page SSR

```tsx
// app/(dashboard)/orders/page.tsx
export const dynamic = 'force-dynamic'

async function OrdersContent() {
  const [user, sellers, companies, statusList] = await Promise.all([
    getCurrentUser(),
    getSellers(),
    getCompanies(),
    getStatusList()
  ])

  return (
    <OrdersClient
      user={user}
      sellers={sellers}
      companies={companies}
      statusList={statusList}
    />
  )
}

export default function OrdersPage() {
  return (
    <PageContainer title="Pedidos" actions={<CreateButton />}>
      <Suspense fallback={<OrdersSkeleton />}>
        <OrdersContent />
      </Suspense>
    </PageContainer>
  )
}
```

## Regras CrГ­ticas

1. **Server Components** para data fetching SSR (sem `'use client'`)
2. **Client Components** para interatividade (`'use client'` no topo)
3. **`force-dynamic`** em pages que precisam de dados frescos
4. **`Suspense`** com fallback skeleton em pages SSR
5. **Types vivem na feature** (`features/{feature}/types/types.ts`), NГѓO no API resource
6. **API Resources re-exportam** types do feature
7. **Imports relativos** dentro da feature (`../types/types`)
8. **Imports absolutos** entre features/libs (`@/lib/api/resources/orders`)
